{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2507","id":3695545313,"node_id":"PR_kwDOEHbxG87cRYvh","html_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2507","diff_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2507.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2507.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2507","number":2507,"state":"closed","locked":false,"title":"lb: improve fn_80027488 matching, tidy a few header signatures","user":{"login":"itsgrimetime","id":990274,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk5MDI3NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/990274?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime","html_url":"https://github.com/itsgrimetime","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"## Summary\n\n- `fn_80027488` in `lbaudio_ax.c`: replaces `lbl_80433710.x194` / `.x274` struct-field accesses with direct references to the standalone extern arrays `lbl_804338A4` and `lbl_80433984` (which live at exactly those addresses per `symbols.txt`), and declares `b` before `a` so MWCC materializes the addresses in the order the original expects.\n- Also tidies a few unrelated lb headers, replacing `UNK_RET` / `UNK_PARAMS` placeholders with the actual `void` signatures the `.c` files already use. Compile-time no-op (those macros already expand to `void`), but makes the headers honest about the ABI.\n\n## Functions matched\n\nNo 100% matches. `fn_80027488` improves **89.55% → 94.86%** fuzzy. The remaining mismatch is one extra prologue instruction from MWCC's register cascade choice — `lis r3/lis r3` for the two HA halves vs `lis r4/lis r3` in the original.\n\n## Files\n\n- `src/melee/lb/lbaudio_ax.c`\n- `src/melee/lb/lb_00F9.h`\n- `src/melee/lb/lb_0192.h`\n- `src/melee/lb/lbcardgame.h`\n\n## Verification\n\n- `python configure.py && ninja` → green (`build/GALE01/main.dol: OK`)\n- No other functions in `lbaudio_ax.c` regressed.","created_at":"2026-05-16T20:55:30Z","updated_at":"2026-05-16T21:24:36Z","closed_at":"2026-05-16T21:24:35Z","merged_at":"2026-05-16T21:24:35Z","merge_commit_sha":"d4891063e12915eeb0e0c60d65ea1b2bd08ee981","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2507/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2507/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2507/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/07bbbd122f74efd582db1d6d9cc246e3dd319f67","head":{"label":"itsgrimetime:pr/lb-audio-and-headers","ref":"pr/lb-audio-and-headers","sha":"07bbbd122f74efd582db1d6d9cc246e3dd319f67","user":{"login":"itsgrimetime","id":990274,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk5MDI3NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/990274?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime","html_url":"https://github.com/itsgrimetime","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/gis